description:
This is a 12 minute workout called '10 Min Guided Meditation For Sleep & Relaxation | Fall Asleep Fast With Soothing Rain Sounds' from the channel Boho Beautiful Yoga.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Sleep Prep and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Relax and fall asleep fast with this 10 minute guided meditation for sleep.  Soothing rain sounds will help your mind relax and help you fall into a deeper and more rejuvenated sleep through this peaceful music and spoken word guidance. 

This guided Boho Beautiful experience is a healing meditation, with spoken suggestions for mind and body relaxation, accompanied with a tranquil soundscape of gentle background sleeping music and calming sound of rain. This is the perfect way to give yourself the opportunity to let go of the day let go of stress, negativity, and worry to welcome a deep and restful sleep.

So find a quiet space, put some headphones on, close your eyes, and enjoy.
